Thu Jun 25 05:54:43 UTC 2026 - Martin Hauke <mardnh@gmx.de>

- Update to version 1.3.7.3.1
  This is a hotfix release for the 1.3.7.3 since there are serious
  bugs were been found and were been fixed.
  * Adjusted the IME start logic to enable it when direct text
    input is enabled.
  * Fixed behaviour of the MD5 algorithm on Big Endian hardware.
  * Fixed a critical bug of checkpoints being reset when
    re-entering normal level from the hub.
  * Fixed TheXTech bug where medals were incorrectly saved after
    death in hub worlds.

